# LaTeX build artifacts — generated externally, not tracked here.
# The canonical source for any test / memo / prac is the .md file.
# PDFs (when produced) are committed; .tex / .aux / .out are not.
*.aux
*.out
*.log
*.toc
*.tex
*.sty
build-*.js

# Compiled binaries
squad
squad.exe
*.exe
*.o
*.obj

# Grader output (generated each run)
grade-report.txt

# Build directories
build/

# Verification artifacts (internal to Swift's build process)
agent-attempt/

# Video scripts are internal recording notes, not student-facing.
# They stay in the local working tree but are not part of the public repo.
**/video-script.md

# Swift Tuition logo image is used by the LaTeX build pipeline locally,
# but does not need to ship in the public student-facing repo.
**/Swift_Tuition_Logo.PNG
**/Swift_Tuition_Logo.png

# Editor / OS files
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
